snippet.textDisplay: I'm a Celtics fan, but the Heat has overall impressed me so much. Nobody ever thought that the Heat would be at the level that they're in, with the 3rd seed in the East so far, and I'm very proud of them. You got Jimmy Butler as a lethal scorer with Tyler Herro as one of the best steals in the draft, and you got Bam Adebayo that has improved his game so much and is a MIP candidate. As a Celtics fan, I might get heated for this, but good job for the Heat and their fans and I wish them all perfect success this season.
